Subject: Re: [T2] ignition trouble

yes,,, look and see if you have a "WR-1" style relay mod...  that relay
controls the starter solenoid.
the new relays have a fuse.. and they do blow

otherwise.. you probably need to clean up connections.. and possibly replace
the ignition electric switch.

Jamie
